                   11:43 12/07/99: Page 1 (HHH) COURTS Axe
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
Triple axe killer Alan Hobbs, 32, of no fixed abode, was jailed for life today
at Reading Crown Court for the murders of Gillian Harvey, 30, Peter Smith, 31,
and Ian Brown, 36, found hacked to death in a flat in Slough, Berks in September
last year.<
